{
  "page": "Raynald Westerling",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Westerling\" title=\"House Westerling\"><img alt=\"House Westerling.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/House_Westerling.svg/50px-House_Westerling.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/House_Westerling.svg/75px-House_Westerling.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/House_Westerling.svg/100px-House_Westerling.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Raynald Westerling</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Westerling\" title=\"House Westerling\"><img alt=\"House Westerling.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/House_Westerling.svg/50px-House_Westerling.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/House_Westerling.svg/75px-House_Westerling.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/House_Westerling.svg/100px-House_Westerling.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Aliases</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li>The seashell knight<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li><li>The knight of seashells<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Westerling\" title=\"House Westerling\">House Westerling</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westermen\" title=\"Westermen\">Westermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\nor before <a href=\"/index.php/282_AC\" title=\"282 AC\">282&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><br />the <a href=\"/index.php/Crag\" title=\"Crag\">Crag</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaf_raynald_westerling.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaf_raynald_westerling.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a> (supposedly)<br />the <a href=\"/index.php/Twins\" title=\"Twins\">Twins</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Gawen_Westerling\" title=\"Gawen Westerling\">Gawen Westerling</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Mother</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Sybell_Spicer\" title=\"Sybell Spicer\">Sybell Spicer</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Raynald Westerling</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Westerling\" title=\"House Westerling\">House Westerling</a>, the eldest son and heir of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Gawen_Westerling\" title=\"Gawen Westerling\">Gawen Westerling</a> and Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Sybell_Spicer\" title=\"Sybell Spicer\">Sybell Spicer</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_For_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast For Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes_by_Raynald\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes by Raynald</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Quotes_about_Raynald\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes about Raynald</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Raynald_Westerling&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Raynald is young and lean, with a thick mop of chestnut hair and a bushy mustache.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> He wears a sand-colored surcoat blazoned with seashells.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Raynald is a cheerful <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Raynald_Westerling&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Raynald_Westerling&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Raynald is part of the entourage of <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/King_in_the_North\" title=\"King in the North\">King in the North</a>, when he returns to <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a> from the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a>, having married Raynald's sister, <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Westerling\" title=\"Jeyne Westerling\">Jeyne</a>. The <a href=\"/index.php/Marriage\" title=\"Marriage\">marriage</a> broke Robb's alliance with <a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a>, as he was to wed a daughter of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Robb enjoys spending time with Raynald; Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a> believes Raynald fills the hole left by the absence of <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When Robb sets out for the <a href=\"/index.php/Twins\" title=\"Twins\">Twins</a> for the marriage of Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Roslin_Frey\" title=\"Roslin Frey\">Roslin Frey</a> and Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure Tully</a>, Raynald is the only <a href=\"/index.php/House_Westerling\" title=\"House Westerling\">Westerling</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Robb%27s_personal_guard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Robb&#39;s personal guard\">accompany</a> him, serving as the royal banner-bearer.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> Arriving at the Twins, <a href=\"/index.php/Grey_Wind\" title=\"Grey Wind\">Grey Wind</a> menaces several Freys, and Robb orders Raynald to put the <a href=\"/index.php/Direwolf\" title=\"Direwolf\">direwolf</a> in a kennel. Catelyn sees this as a deft move, as Robb has removed the Westerling from the jealous Freys' sight.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> Robb is betrayed and killed by Houses Frey and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bolton\" title=\"House Bolton\">Bolton</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Wedding\" title=\"Red Wedding\">Red Wedding</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_For_Crows\"><i>A Feast For Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Raynald_Westerling&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast For Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>According to his mother, Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Sybell_Spicer\" title=\"Sybell Spicer\">Sybell Spicer</a>, Raynald was unaware of the arrangement she and her brother, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Rolph_Spicer\" title=\"Rolph Spicer\">Rolph Spicer</a>, had with Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a>. Sybell informs Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a> Raynald should have joy of marry a bride from <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a>. Jaime understands this as Tywin intended to marry Raynald to his <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> niece, <a href=\"/index.php/Joy_Hill\" title=\"Joy Hill\">Joy Hill</a>. The notion of her son marrying a bastard upsets Sybell.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> However, according to a semi-canon source, this is a misunderstanding on Jaime's part<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafjoy_hill.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafjoy_hill.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup> as Tywin already arranged for Joy to marry one of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a>'s natural sons.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>After the resolution of the <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Riverrun\" title=\"Siege of Riverrun\">siege of Riverrun</a>, Ser Jaime Lannister asks about Raynald's fate. <a href=\"/index.php/Edwyn_Frey\" title=\"Edwyn Frey\">Edwyn Frey</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Rivers\" title=\"Walder Rivers\">Walder Rivers</a> reveal that Raynald surrendered his sword to Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Whalen_Frey\" title=\"Whalen Frey\">Whalen Frey</a>, but then freed Grey Wind from his chains in the stables when several Frey men-at-arms tried to kill the direwolf. While doing so, Raynald was hit by a crossbow bolt and fell into the <a href=\"/index.php/Green_Fork\" title=\"Green Fork\">Green Fork</a>. Raynald's body was not identified among the thousand corpses afterward, but his trail of blood led to the river's steps.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Raynald_Westerling&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Gawen_Westerling\" title=\"Gawen Westerling\">Gawen</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Sybell_Spicer\" title=\"Sybell Spicer\">Sybell<br />Spicer</a></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"></td></tr><tr align=\"cent